{
  "stem": "7282.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From, from there-- from on the Moskva, they sent-- they sent us farther.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't send us back--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not long, maybe two months or so-- not, not, not long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They haven't got time for it--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or what.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us-- they, they took us and sent us on, on the Russian side, deep in Russia, to recuperate and to prepare to send you on the front line.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH], the, the villages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not villages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's big cities, [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there we stood, I don't know, maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two or three months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they sent us back on to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And since then, when we start advancing-- we beat them up and we start advancing from Stalingrad, they've been running.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans had been running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we'd been running after them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went from there all the time in the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's been back to Poland-- I went back to Poland and went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got on the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on to Rostock before-- 20 kilometers before Berlin-- on the Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and there is-- I, I stood there till the end of the war, almost-- there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I mean-- So you were there a couple of years?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I mean, it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We been there in '44, '45, what-- and still in the army, till we got-- when, when, when the war ended.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Berlin it was-- I don't remember what day, what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We've been on, on, on the-- on the Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it was the battles-- back when we-- when we drove them back already, we went into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed in Warsaw maybe about three months.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
